high_descs: turn around and walk to the near end of the room, but stop just short to turn right and walk to the kitchen stove on the right
grab a clear bowl out of the cabinet above the microwave which is above the stove
turn around and walk forward to the fridge up ahead
place the bowl inside of the fridge, let it cool, then take it back out
turn around and walk back over to the microwave above the stove
place the bowl inside of the microwave
anns.task_desc: place a cooled clear bowl inside the microwave

high_descs: Turn around, take a right after the fridge, walk up to the stove, and look up above the stove at the cabinets above the microwave.
Open the cabinet on the left, pick up the glass bowl, close the door.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge door, place the bowl in the fridge to the right of the mug, close the door, open the door, take out the bowl, close the door.
Walk back over to the stove and look up at the microwave above the stove.
Open the microwave door, place the glass bowl in the microwave, and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Chill a glass bowl and place it in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around, walk to the white stove on the right and look up at the microwave.
Open the left side of the middle cabinet, pick up the clear container and close the door.
Turn right and walk to the black fridge on the right.
Put the clear container on the middle shelf inside the fridge, chill it, remove it and close the door.
Turn right, walk to the stove on the right and look up at the microwave.
Put the chilled container inside the microwave and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled container in a microwave.
